Installing CircuitPython libraries
----------------------------------
Needed to drive the PiTFT display.
Follow instructions at this Adafruit tutorial:
https://learn.adafruit.com/circuitpython-on-raspberrypi-linux/installing-circuitpython-on-raspberry-pi

Run the test program:
  > python3 blinktest.py


Python programming the PiTFT display
------------------------------------
Following instructions at this Adafruit tutorial:
  https://learn.adafruit.com/adafruit-mini-pitft-135x240-color-tft-add-on-for-raspberry-pi/python-setup

Run the test program:
  > sudo python3 rgb_display_minipitfttest.py

Run the stats program:
  > sudo python3 pistats.py
